"`decode_context_parallel_size`, refer to the following example:"
msgstr ""
"您可以通过 `prefill_context_parallel_size` 和 `decode_context_parallel_size` 启用 "
"`PCP` 和 `DCP`，参考以下示例："

msgid "- Offline example:"
msgstr "- 离线示例："

msgid "- Online example:"
msgstr "- 在线示例："

msgid ""
"The total world size is `tensor_parallel_size` * "
"`prefill_context_parallel_size`, so the examples above need 4 NPUs for each."
msgstr ""
"总世界大小为 `tensor_parallel_size` * "
"`prefill_context_parallel_size`，因此上述每个示例需要4个NPU。"

msgid "## Constraints"
msgstr "## 约束条件"

msgid ""
"- While using DCP, the following constraints must be met:\n"
"    - For MLA-based model, such as DeepSeek-R1:\n"
"        - `tensor_parallel_size >= decode_context_parallel_size`\n"
"        - `tensor_parallel_size % decode_context_parallel_size == 0`\n"
"    - For GQA-based model, such as Qwen3-235B:\n"
"        - `(tensor_parallel_size // num_key_value_heads) >= decode_context_parallel_size`\n"
"        - `(tensor_parallel_size // num_key_value_heads) % decode_context_parallel_size == 0`"
msgstr ""
"- 使用DCP时，必须满足以下约束条件：\n"
"    - 对于基于MLA的模型，例如DeepSeek-R1：\n"
"        - `tensor_parallel_size >= decode_context_parallel_size`\n"
"        - `tensor_parallel_size % decode_context_parallel_size == 0`\n"
"    - 对于基于GQA的模型，例如Qwen3-235B：\n"
"        - `(tensor_parallel_size // num_key_value_heads) >= decode_context_parallel_size`\n"
"        - `(tensor_parallel_size // num_key_value_heads) % decode_context_parallel_size == 0`"

msgid ""
"- While using Context Parallel in KV cache transfer-needed scenario (e.g. KV"
" pooling, PD disaggregation), to simplify KV cache transmission, "
"`cp_kv_cache_interleave_size` must be set to the same value of KV cache "
"`block_size`(default: 128), which specifies CP to split KV cache in a block-"
"interleave style. For example:"
msgstr ""
"- 在需要KV缓存传输的场景（例如KV池化、PD分离）中使用上下文并行时，为简化KV缓存传输，`cp_kv_cache_interleave_size`"
" 必须设置为与KV缓存 `block_size`（默认值：128）相同的值，该参数指定CP以块交错方式分割KV缓存。例如："

